      <description>&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Is normalization good?
    &lt;div id=&#34;is-normalization-good&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    
    &lt;span
        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;
        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#is-normalization-good&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;
    
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Yes and no, it depends&amp;hellip;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img
    class=&#34;my-0 rounded-md&#34;
    loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
    decoding=&#34;async&#34;
