&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The normalization and harmonization of data is something I consider essential, it ensures that information can be read quickly&amp;hellip;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Although sometimes, when you come across data that&amp;rsquo;s too structured, like, I don&amp;rsquo;t know, &lt;a
  href=&#34;https://knowledge-base.inspire.ec.europa.eu/index_en&#34;
    target=&#34;_blank&#34;
  &gt;INSPIRE&lt;/a&gt; :eyes:, you lose track of it, to the point where it seems complicated, just because needs to be&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
